1. rotate function 
    rotate, rotateX, rotateY, rotateZ, rotate3d

2. scale function = zooming
    scale, scaleX, scaleY, scaleZ, scale3d 

3. skew function = strech type
    skew, skewX, skewY 

4. translate function = movement
    translate, translateX, translateY, translateZ, translate3d

5. matrix function 
    matrix, matrix3d

6. perspective function = view 
    perspective

    for 3d : https://ramlmn.github.io/visualizing-matrix3d/